      <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
       Now, anyone with internet access and a web
browser can enjoy
       <b>
        reading
       </b>
       <a href="#footnote_2" id="footnote_source_2">
        <sup class="mark" style="font-size: 115%">
         2
        </sup>
       </a>
       a high quality up-to-date copy of Feynman's legendary lectures.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
       This edition has been
designed for ease of reading on devices of any size or shape; text, figures and equations can all be
zoomed without degradation.
       <a href="#footnote_3" id="footnote_source_3">
        <sup class="mark" style="font-size: 115%">
         3
        </sup>
       </a>
      </p>
